            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-mono mt-1">github.com/EduMyna/EduMyna.com/blob/main/FOUNDER_STORY_DECK.md</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Content Files -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-slate-200">Content Files</h2>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div>
            <a href="https://github.com/EduMyna/EduMyna.com/blob/main/src/pages/story.astro" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">story.astro ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Evolution story page source (with real photos)</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-mono mt-1">github.com/EduMyna/EduMyna.com/blob/main/src/pages/story.astro</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <a href="https://github.com/EduMyna/EduMyna.com/blob/main/src/pages/founder-story.astro" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">founder-story.astro ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">About Gautam credibility page source</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-mono mt-1">github.com/EduMyna/EduMyna.com/blob/main/src/pages/founder-story.astro</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <a href="https://github.com/EduMyna/EduMyna.com/blob/main/src/pages/pitch.astro" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">pitch.astro ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Section 8 pitch deck page source</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-mono mt-1">github.com/EduMyna/EduMyna.com/blob/main/src/pages/pitch.astro</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <a href="https://github.com/EduMyna/EduMyna.com/blob/main/src/pages/team-deck.astro" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">team-deck.astro ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Team recruitment deck page source</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-mono mt-1">github.com/EduMyna/EduMyna.com/blob/main/src/pages/team-deck.astro</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <a href="https://github.com/EduMyna/EduMyna.com/blob/main/src/content/blog/what-12-years-building-edtech-taught-me.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">what-12-years-building-edtech-taught-me.md ↗</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Blog post source file</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-mono mt-1">github.com/EduMyna/EduMyna.com/blob/main/src/content/blog/what-12-years-building-edtech-taught-me.md</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Media Coverage -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-slate-200">Media Coverage & Press</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-6">Chronological collection of media stories about the journey (2013-2019)</p>

        <!-- 2013: BBC Coverage -->
        <div class="mb-8">
          <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-slate-400 mb-2">2012-2014 - Startup Village Era</p>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
              <a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/business-22205601" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">BBC Business - India's 'Silicon Coast' ↗</a>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">BBC coverage of Startup Village as India's first PPP incubator building Kerala's "Silicon Coast"</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
              <a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/av/business-22210389" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">BBC Video - Startup Village Feature ↗</a>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">BBC video coverage of the physical incubator and student entrepreneurship programs</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
              <p class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-1">A Company that Mentors Young Entrepreneurs | A 'school' for startups</p>
              <div class="flex gap-3 mt-2">
                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LCsQ68plQos" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-sm text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">YouTube ↗</a>
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1234205526639360&id=417921431601111&_rdr" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-sm text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Facebook ↗</a>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-2">Documentary-style feature on Startup Village's mentorship model</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
              <a href="https://www.siliconindia.com/shownews/www.siliconindia.com/shownews/indias-first-startup-village-at-kochi-nid-103361-cid-100.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Silicon India - India's First Startup Village at Kochi ↗</a>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Tech industry coverage of India's pioneering PPP incubator model</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
              <a href="https://www.thenewsminute.com/news/kochi-startup-village-countrys-best-46936" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">The News Minute - Kochi Startup Village: Country's Best ↗</a>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Regional news coverage of Startup Village's achievements and impact</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
              <a href="https://www.indiascienceandtechnology.gov.in/innovations/incubators/startup-village-kochi" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">India Science & Technology Portal - Startup Village ↗</a>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Official Government of India portal listing Startup Village as a key incubator</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
              <a href="https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/startup-village" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Crunchbase - Startup Village Profile ↗</a>
