            </div>
            <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
              <a href="https://www.business-standard.com/article/pti-stories/kerala-s-startup-village-ranked-india-s-best-incubator-116072201221_1.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Business Standard - India's Best Incubator ↗</a>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Business Standard coverage of the #1 ranking achievement</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
              <a href="https://blog.sv.co/startup-village-ranked-1-amongst-indian-incubators-b78b5b281572" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">SV.CO Blog - Ranked #1 Announcement ↗</a>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Official announcement and reflection on achieving #1 incubator status</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 2016: Going Digital -->
        <div class="mb-8">
          <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-slate-400 mb-2">2016 - Digital Transformation</p>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
              <p class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-1">Economic Times - Startup Village COO talks about going completely digital</p>
              <div class="flex gap-3 mt-2 flex-wrap">
                <a href="https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/et-now/tech/startup-village-coo-talks-about-going-completely-digital/videoshow/53161490.cms" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-sm text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">ET Article ↗</a>
