            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 mb-4">First-hand accounts, stories, and updates from the SV.CO team (2016-2018)</p>

          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="bg-white border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4">
