            <div class="bg-white border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4">
              <a href="https://medium.com/sv-co-blog/startup-village-ranked-1-amongst-indian-incubators-b78b5b281572" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Startup Village ranked #1 amongst Indian Incubators (July 2016) ↗</a>
