              <a href="https://medium.com/sv-co-blog/learning-startup-basics-with-sv-co-d781dbe8409d" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Learning startup basics with SV.CO (October 2017) ↗</a>
